  <section>
    <h2>Keyboard Support</h2>
    <table class="props-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Key</th>
          <th>Action</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><kbd>?</kbd></td><td>Open/close the shortcuts overlay</td></tr>
        <tr><td><kbd>Escape</kbd></td><td>Close the overlay</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>The <kbd>?</kbd> hotkey does <strong>not</strong> fire when focus is inside an input, textarea, or content-editable element.</p>
